1.0.0.description: IBM Watson® AIOps for IBM Cloud Pak® for Data provides holistic insights that help prioritize issues and resolution efforts that take place in ever-evolving hybrid cloud and traditional IT environments. It identifies and gathers signals across a variety of structured and unstructured data channels  including alerts  logs  and tickets.
